· Task: Surface following with varying materials (sandpaper, foam, metal).
· Compare against PID and frozen RL baselines.

Phase 3: Full Contact-Rich Manipulation

· Task: Peg insertion, USB plugging, or delicate food handling.
· Evaluate success rate, force overshoot, and adaptation speed.

Phase 4: Long-Term Autonomous Adaptation

· Deploy for extended periods (hours/days) in a changing environment.
· Measure drift in KL divergence D_{\text{KL}}(Q \| P) and residual policy magnitude.

